title: Global Capitalism-Monthly Economic Update-Richard D Wolff-Jan 20
description:
Global Capitalism-Monthly Economic Update-Richard D Wolff-Jan 2016

Published on January 14, 2016


Capitalism Delivers the...: Inequality, Instability, Insecurity

Co-sponsored by Democracy at Work, Left Forum, and Judson Memorial Church

These programs begin with 30 minutes of short updates on important economic events of the last month. Then Wolff analyzes several major economic issues. For January these will include:


    Stock Markets from China to New York: Dangers Looming in 2016
    Deadly Oil Economics: Iran, Saudi Arabia, and Middle East Wars
    Obamacare and the "Medical-Industrial Complex": Troubling Economics
